OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FITV News Midlands Correspondent Ben
OL,7,FChapman was invited on a Home Office
OL,8,Fraid targeting illegal workers as the
OL,9,FGovernment aims to show it is serious
OL,10,Fabout immigration
OL,12,FNet migration to the UK is estimated
OL,13,Fto have halved from 860,000 in the
OL,14,Fyear ending December 2023 to 431,000
OL,15,Fin the year ending December 2024, the
OL,16,FOffice for National Statistics said.
