OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FThis is the biggest calendar-year drop
OL,7,Fsince the early stages of the
OL,8,Fpandemic, when net migration fell from
OL,9,F184,000 in the year ending December
OL,10,F2019 to 93,000 in the year ending
OL,11,FDecember 2020.
OL,13,FThe latest decrease is the largest
OL,14,Fnumerical drop for any 12-month period
OL,15,Fand the ONS said the decline has been
OL,16,Fdriven by falling numbers of people
OL,17,Fcoming to work and study in the UK.
