OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FDirector of population statistics at
OL,7,Fthe ONS Mary Gregory said: "Our
OL,8,Fprovisional estimates show net
OL,9,Fmigration has almost halved compared
OL,10,Fwith the previous year, driven by
OL,11,Ffalling numbers of people coming to
OL,12,Fwork and study, particularly student
OL,13,Fdependants. This follows policy
OL,14,Fchanges brought in restricting visa
OL,15,Fapplications.
