OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FThe figures come less than two weeks
OL,7,Fafter Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fblamed migration for "incalculable"
OL,9,Fdamage to British society.
OL,11,FIn a speech on immigration policy, the
OL,12,Fprime minister set out a range of
OL,13,Fmeasures aimed at reducing the numbers
OL,14,Ffurther, warning the UK risked
OL,15,Fbecoming an "island of strangers" if
OL,16,Fpeople failed to integrate better.
