OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FSir Keir's plan includes reforming
OL,7,Fwork and study visas and requiring a
OL,8,Fhigher level of English across all
OL,9,Fimmigration routes, and is expected to
OL,10,Freduce the number of people coming to
OL,11,Fthe UK by up to 100,000 per year -
OL,12,Falthough the PM refused to set a
OL,13,Ftarget level for migration figures.
OL,15,FHis speech and use of language drew
OL,16,Fcriticism from some, who compared the
OL,17,Ftone to that of Enoch Powell's
OL,18,Finfamous 1968 "rivers of blood" speech.
