OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FThe prime minister and government
OL,7,Fministers rejected this analogy, with
OL,8,FYvette Cooper insisting the tone was
OL,9,F"completely different".
OL,11,FFor many years the amount of people
OL,12,Fcoming to the UK has been higher than
OL,13,Fthose leaving. The government's latest
OL,14,Fpromise to "take back control of our
OL,15,Fborders" is seen by many as a response
OL,16,Fto the anti-immigration policies of
OL,17,FReform UK who have been surging in
OL,18,Fopinion polls following local election
OL,19,Fsuccesses.
